why are you what's

00:03:23.441 --> 00:03:24.441
what's going on here

00:03:24.442 --> 00:03:26.721
like tell me more about this

00:03:26.722 --> 00:03:30.481
so that's research that's really exciting and needs to happen

00:03:30.482 --> 00:03:32.641
but I would love to hear your thoughts on this

00:03:32.642 --> 00:03:35.021
I'm super fascinated by these findings

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.820
and I think that they probably have a lot of um

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:40.420
importance for the upcoming election

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:43.600
